): BMNH (E) 1626923, male, Bhutan. 95-37.v.96, 
<taxonomicName id="F50A71A502086C3D8E44A9347AF35DF6" class="Insecta" family="Pyralidae" genus="Sybrida" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Sybrida pallescens" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="139" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pallescens">
